    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1944-09-03T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1944-09-03T00:00:00-05:00" n="133"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d133">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">865.48/9–144: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">President</gloss> to the President’s
                        Personal Representative at Vatican City</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Taylor</hi>
                    </persName>)<note n="1" xml:id="d133fn1">Sent to the Commanding General, Allied
                        Force Headquarters, Italy, via Army channels, with instructions to pass to
                        Taylor at Vatican City.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">top secret</hi>
                    </seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1944-09-03">3 September
                            1944</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Please ask General O’Dwyer to report to me as soon as possible, preferably
                    Washington by Friday morning,<note n="2" xml:id="d133fn2">September 8.</note> or
                    if he cannot make this then in Quebec on Monday morning the eleventh.<note n="3"
                        xml:id="d133fn3">O’Dwyer reached Washington in time to see the President at
                        11:15 a.m., September 8. See <hi rend="italic">post</hi>, <ref
                            target="#pg_210">p. 210</ref>.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Roosevelt</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
